<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">How the Investment Works</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center text-muted">
      Simple mechanics. No promises. Full transparency.
    </p>

    <div class="steps-list">
      <div class="step-item">
        <span class="step-num">01</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Invest together as aligned stewards</h3>
          <p>
            A small group of investors co-acquires ownership of the property. We are
            looking for people who are drawn to the mission and the community, not only
            the financial case. The legal structure, minimum investment, and ownership
            mechanics are defined in the investor agreement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <span class="step-num">02</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Years 1 to 5: reinvest and build</h3>
          <p>
            During the first five years, operating income from the property is targeted
            to be reinvested into upgrades, infrastructure, land stewardship, and guest
            experience. The aim is to increase the property's long-term value before any
            income is distributed to investors. This is the designed intention, subject
            to final legal documentation and actual operating conditions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <span class="step-num">03</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Investor priority during the village season</h3>
          <p>
            Investors receive priority access to reserve stays for up to 4 months per
            year, typically during the peak village season from December through April.
            The priority booking window opens first for investors. Any remaining
            availability then opens to the broader community. Exact reservation rules
            will be defined in the investor agreement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <span class="step-num">04</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Long-term value from land, brand, and community</h3>
          <p>
            The long-term value of this investment is designed to come from three
            sources: the land and its location in Florianópolis, improved revenue
            capacity as the property is developed, and the gravity of a real community
            and brand. None of this is guaranteed. Real estate involves risk.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="investment-disclaimer">
      <p>
        <strong>Disclosure:</strong> Not investment advice. Details are subject to legal
        documentation and local regulations. Real estate values can decrease. Operating
        businesses can underperform. Regulatory environments change. Currency fluctuations
        affect the value of your investment in your home currency. Always conduct independent
        due diligence with qualified legal and financial advisors before making any decision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .steps-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .step-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    align-items: start;
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.35;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .investment-disclaimer {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .investment-disclaimer p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .investment-disclaimer strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
